snippet: A lawmaker from the party of the ousted Ukrainian president was attacked Tuesday by a crowd in the Black Sea port of Odessa during campaigning for a parliamentary election set for Oct. 26.
abstract: Ukrainian lawmaker Nestor I Shufrich is attacked by crowd in Odessa during campaigning for October parliamentary election; Shufrich is a member of same party as ousted president Viktor F Yanukovych and defender of pro-Russian rebels in eastern Ukraine.
lead_paragraph: A lawmaker from the party of the ousted Ukrainian president was attacked Tuesday by a crowd in the Black Sea port of Odessa during campaigning for a parliamentary election set for Oct. 26.

headline.main: Ukraine: Politician Is Attacked While Campaigning
headline.print_headline: Ukraine: Politician Is Attacked While Campaigning
